            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) Anno ab incarnacione domini nostri Iesu Christi millesimo nonaiesimo,
                        quinto idus septimber indicione terciadecima, <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Monks #Missus #Offersio/donatio #Cells/hermitages #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benediciti sito inter Padum et
                            Larionem</orgName>. Ego <persName
                            key="Count #childOf #marriage #Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Cells/hermitages #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#people/2181">Ubertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName key="#parentOf"
                            ref="#people/2149">Arduini</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Count" ref="#places/53">Parmensis</placeName>, qui profesus
                        sum lege vivere <rs key="#Lombard">Langobardorum</rs> presentibus disi:
                        Quisquis in sanctis ac venerabilibus locis ex suis aliquit contulerit rebus
                        iusta octori vocem in oc seculo centuplum accipiat, insuper quod melius est
                        vita posidebit etenam. Ideoque ego qui supra Ubertus dono et ofero pro anima
                        mea et <rs key="#marriage">conius</rs> mea et <rs key="#childOf">filio</rs>
                        meo atque <rs key="#parentOf">parentorum</rs> meorum mercede in pre iam
                        nominatum monasterium in <persName key="#Monks #Missus"><name
                                ref="Hubaldus/monachus">Ubaldus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Monks #Missus"><name ref="Petrus/monachus"
                            >Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monahis</rs> et <rs key="#Missus">misis</rs> eiusdem
                        monasterii; oc est <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">capella</rs> una edificata et
                        consecrata in onore <orgName key="#Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2004">Sancti Iusti</orgName> poxita in <rs
                            key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle #Cells/hermitages" ref="#places/2475"
                            >Medule</placeName> cum omnibus rebus sibi pertinentibus tam intus quam
                        et de foris. Insuper donavit de suis propris rebus, oc est <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">braide et aliis terris</rs> quod est per
                        mensura super totum <rs key="#Size">iuias centum</rs> sicut est desinatu per
                        suos misos, hi sunt <persName><name ref="Rodelandus/de Lucera"
                                >Urlandus</name></persName> de <placeName>Lucera</placeName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Rustichellus">Rustichelo</name></persName> et
                        ceteri. Eo tinore anc mea ofersionem facio quamdiu monasterium Sancti
                        Benedicti manet sub regimine monasterii <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2091">Sancti Petri</orgName>
                        <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/2723">Clungniacensis</placeName>
                        abeat et posideat ipsas res; et si eveneri quod deceserit de gimine
                        cluniacensis monasterii deveniant ipse res in proprio iure cluniacensis
                        monasterii. Ab ac die predictum monasterium dono cedo trado confero et per
                        presente <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam ofersionis</rs> at abendum
                        confinno faciendum; confirmo faciendum exinde a presenti die pars ipsum
                        monasterium aut cui pars ipsum monasterium dederit <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">iure proprietario</rs> quicquit
                        voluerit sine omni mea qui supra Uberto et eheredibus meis contradicione.
                        Quidem espondeo atque promitto me ego qui supra Ubertus una cum [m]eis
                        eheredibus tibi predictum monasterio aut cui ipsum monasterium dederit
                        suprascriptis rebus simul cum predicta capella in integro ab omni omine
                        defensare promitto; quod si defendere non potuerimus aut si vobis exinde
                        aliquit per covis inienium subtraere quexierimus tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in
                            duplum</rs> eadem mea donacionem ut supra leitur vobis restituamus sicut
                        pro tempore fuerint melioratis predictis rebus aut valuerit sub estimacione
                        in consimilibus locis. Anc enim cartulam ofersionis <persName
                            key="#Notary #Writer #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Albertus/notarius"
                                >Albertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domini reis tradidit et scribere rogavi in
                        qua subter confirmans <rs key="#Witness">testibus</rs>que obtulit
                        roborandum. Actum intus <placeName key="#Fortress" ref="#places/2944"
                            >Roka</placeName> feliciter. Signum manus suprascripto Uberto qui anc
                        cartulam ofersionis fieri rogavit ut supra. Ubertus comes subscripsi. Signum
                        manibus <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #Lombard"><name
                                ref="Bernardus">Bernardo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #Lombard"><name ref="Marchesus"
                                >Markeso</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #Lombard"><name ref="Bonus"
                            >Bono</name></persName> testes rogati viventes Langobardorum lege. (S.)
                        Ego qui supra Albertus notarius domini regis rogatus <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scripsi</rs> post tradita complevi et dedi. <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3758"/> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2947">Dallo</placeName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3759"/> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2948">Camuriana</placeName> interfuerunt. </ab>
